      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRIVIA (1) is better than last start when sixth (22.65) in a NG at this track over 375m. Has a good record at this journey. Has a strong record out of this box with five wins and a minor placing from 12 starts. Should be very hard to beat this time. COCO DAVIES (8) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at Wagga over 320m behind Lagoon Ohiyesa (20.19) in a Grade 4/5. Has never missed the frame from four starts from this draw, including a win. Cannot be taken lightly. SONALI (2) is a well performed dog and winner of seven races who is worth forgiving after finishing out of the placings at Nowra (21.30). The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Bold showing expected. ZIPPING TAMIKA (5) drops in journey and is worth considering.",
